N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 163.1 - Radio home-study courses

State Regulations
(a) The
department may establish and conduct radio home-study courses. (b) A fee of $5 shall be charged each
nonresident of the State enrolled in a radio home-study course conducted by the
department. Notes
